## âš  Important Notes

* zBox is intended for **advanced users** who want rapid, modular environment deployment without editing every file manually.
* System thinkers and tweakers can load **custom environments** directly via the zBox CLI.

**Description**
zBox enables quick deployment across Linux-based machines, keeping your environments up to date without tedious manual configuration.

**Author Notes**
zBox was designed for low-level system thinkers. If you struggle with advanced KEY\:VALUE pairing, there may be a learning curve.
Its main strength is fast & easy environment management with **custom environments on the fly** via the zBox CLI.

